OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FA council has offered an explanation
OL,7,Fafter almost 20 trees were chopped
OL,8,Fdown in the grounds of Newark Castle.
OL,10,FA total of 16 trees and some shrubs
OL,11,Fwere removed from the grounds last
OL,12,Fmonth in order to make the site more
OL,13,Fwelcoming and create new paths for
OL,14,Feasy access, the authority said.
OL,16,FHowever, there has still been
OL,17,Fconfusion over why it was necessary
OL,18,Ffor the trees to be removed, some even
OL,19,Fdescribing it as a "betrayal".
