OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FThe council has confirmed that these
OL,7,Ftree works were carried out as part of
OL,8,Fthe preparation work for the Gatehouse
OL,9,FProject at the castle, with building
OL,10,Fwork expected to start in early 2025.
OL,12,FThe project will create the original
OL,13,FRomanesque Gatehouse reinstated as the
OL,14,Fentrance to the castle.
OL,16,FThe new entrance will make the castle
OL,17,Fmore accessible and it will also
OL,18,Finclude a new facility beneath the
OL,19,Fgatehouse bridge for learning visits
OL,20,Fand community groups.
