OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FCouncillor Emma Oldham, Portfolio
OL,7,FHolder for Climate and the Environment
OL,8,Fexplained that the decision was not
OL,9,Ftaken lightly and that "much careful
OL,10,Fdeliberation" was put into the plans
OL,11,Fto ensure it made the area more
OL,12,Faccessible, but also preserved the
OL,13,Farchaeology and remained an attractive
OL,14,Fplace for wildlife.
