OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FShe added: "We have worked with
OL,7,Fexperts, commissioning an independent
OL,8,Ftree impact report and separate
OL,9,Fbiodiversity report to support the
OL,10,Fproject's development and this shows
OL,11,Fthat with the removal of these trees,
OL,12,Fmany of which are young and self-
OL,13,Fseeded, the project will see a
OL,14,Fbiodiversity net gain due to the
OL,15,Finclusion of more colourful, wildlife-
OL,16,Ffriendly shrubs, hedges and nectar-
OL,17,Frich planting."
