OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FThese trees were removed between
OL,7,FMonday, November 18 and Wednesday,
OL,8,FNovember 20, and where possible logs
OL,9,Fand tree stems have been retained on
OL,10,Fthe site and used as habitat piles or
OL,11,Fplay features.
OL,13,FIt is also hoped that the council will
OL,14,Freplant an equal number of trees in
OL,15,Fthe area, potentially the nearby
OL,16,FRiverside Park, and more wildlife-
OL,17,Ffriendly shrubs and hedges will also
OL,18,Fbe planted.
