OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FInstead, they are prioritising
OL,7,Finvestment and financial interests
OL,8,Fover their commitment to the
OL,9,Fenvironment and the wishes of the
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,F"These trees were sacrificed for a
OL,13,Fproject that nobody asked for and
OL,14,Fnobody truly wanted.
OL,16,F"This plan was originally drawn up
OL,17,Fbefore the Covid-19 pandemic by the
OL,18,Fprevious administration however, it's
OL,19,Fbeen made clear by residence that
OL,20,Ftheir priorities have now changed."
