OL,3,CWhy a council ordered almost 20 trees
OL,4,Cto be chopped down on castle grounds
OL,6,FHe added: "Residents voted for these
OL,7,Fcouncillors to stand up for the
OL,8,Fenvironment, but many now feel utterly
OL,9,Flet down by this broken pledge."
OL,11,FFollowing the trees being cut, a drop
OL,12,Fin session was held by the Council at
OL,13,Fthe grounds to answer any questions
OL,14,Ffrom the public about the matter.
